<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Accueil</title>

  <style>
    body {
      background-color: black;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .terminal-box {
      background-color: black;
      color: #00ff00;
      font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 2px solid #00ff00;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px #00ff00;
      max-width: 600px;
    }

    .terminal-box h1 {
      color: #00ff00;
    }

    .btn {
      display: block;
      margin: 10px 0;
      padding: 10px;
      color: #00ff00;
      border: 1px solid #00ff00;
      text-decoration: none;
      width: fit-content;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background: #00ff00;
      color: black;
    }

    .cursor {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 100vw;
      height: 100vw;
      background: #00ff00;
      margin-left: 5px;
      animation: blink 1s infinite;
    }

    @keyframes blink {
      50% { opacity: 0; }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="terminal-box">

  <h1>&gt; Accueil<span class="cursor"></span></h1>

  <p>Étudiant en cybersécurité web spécialisé en pentesting.</p>

